                   syriaca-tags="#syriaca-headword #syriaca-anglicized">Three Brothers (text)</title>
            <author xml:lang="fr" source="#bib544-1">Jérôme et Enanicho</author>
            <note xml:lang="syr" type="incipit" source="#bib544-1">
               <quote>ܚܙܝܢܢ ܕܝܢ ܬܡܢ ܐܦ ܬܠܬܐ ܐܚ̈ܐ ܕܪܕܝܢ ܗܘ̣ܘ ܒܡܠܬܐ...</quote>
            </note>
            <note xml:lang="fr" type="incipit" source="#bib544-1">
               <quote>Nous y vîmes aussi trois frères qui étaient instruits en parole…</quote>
            </note>
            <note xml:lang="syr" type="explicit" source="#bib544-1">
               <quote>ܐܝܟ ܕܐܢܫ ܡܟܝܠ ܠܐ ܢܫܚܘܩ ܐܢܘܢ.</quote>
            </note>
            <note xml:lang="fr" type="explicit" source="#bib544-1">
               <quote>pour que personne ne les opprimât plus.</quote>
            </note>
            <note type="editions">
